# Unity generated folders
[Ll]ibrary/
[Tt]emp/
[Oo]bj/
[Bb]uild/
[Bb]uilds/
[Ll]ogs/
[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/
MemoryCaptures/
Recordings/

# Unity crash log
crash.log
*.stacktrace

# Asset store plugin cache
/[Aa]sset [Ss]tore-5.x/

# NOTE: .meta files MUST be tracked — do not add *.meta here
# Unity uses .meta files to store GUIDs and import settings

# Visual Studio / Rider / VS Code
.vs/
.idea/
*.csproj
*.sln
*.suo
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db
*.pidb.meta
*.pdb.meta
*.mdb.meta

# Rider
.idea/

# OS generated
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Build artifacts
*.apk
*.aab
*.unitypackage
*.app
*.exe
*.x86
*.x86_64
*.dll

# IL2CPP
Il2CppOutputProject/

# Packages — restored on demand, do not commit
# (keep Packages/manifest.json and Packages/packages-lock.json tracked)
/[Pp]ackages/*/
!/[Pp]ackages/manifest.json
!/[Pp]ackages/packages-lock.json
